orate core, commercial lending, payments, liquidity management, investments, virtual accounts, trade and supply chain finance, receivables and collections, treasury, corporate procurement exchange, and corporate banking exchange. Further, it offers consumer banking, including core banking, lending, cards, and digital engagement; quantum; wealth management; capital markets, such as brokerage and securities; insurance, such as magic submission, risk analyst, and underwriting; bank treasury; governance risk and compliance, as well as ESG edge; and accounts payable, procurement management, and retail solutions. The company develops IntellectAI's Purple Fabric an open business impact AI platform that delivers secure, decision-grade intelligence with measurable business impact; eMACH.ai, an open finance platform which focuses on finance operations; iTurmeric, an integration and configuration platform; and Academic TeamSpace, an AI collaboration platform for the education sector. It serves retail and corporate customers, banks, wealth managers, private bankers, card issuers, as well as capital market participants such as brokers, custodians, asset managers, insurance carriers, government enterprises, corporates and retail chains, and educational institutions. Intellect Design Arena Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Chennai, India."}}